patthana8.5:1.1_0: Nahetuñceva nahetuvippayuttañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca dhammo
patthana8.5:1.1_1: uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nahetuñceva nahetuvippayuttañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetuvippayutto
patthana8.5:1.1_2: ceva na nahetu ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nahetuñceva nahetuvippayuttañca dhammaṁ
patthana8.5:1.1_3: paṭicca nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca nahetuvippayutto ceva na nahetu ca dhammā
patthana8.5:2.1_0: Nahetuvippayuttañceva na nahetuñca dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetuvippayutto ceva na nahetu
patthana8.5:2.1_1: ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nahetuvippayuttañceva na nahetuñca dhammaṁ paṭicca
patthana8.5:2.1_2: nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nahetuvippayuttañceva
patthana8.5:2.1_3: na nahetuñca dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca nahetuvippayutto ceva
patthana8.5:2.1_4: na nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana8.5:3.1: Nahetuñceva nahetuvippayuttañca nahetuvippayuttañceva na nahetuñca dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
